    data={[
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do I need to know coding to use an AI website builder?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "No coding required. AI website builders are no-code platforms designed for complete beginners. Everything is visual drag-and-drop or AI-generated. You answer questions or provide a prompt, the AI builds your site. Customization happens through visual editors - no HTML, CSS, or JavaScript needed. Whether you're 15 or 75, tech-savvy or tech-phobic, AI builders work the same way. The AI handles all technical aspects automatically."
