        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What if I don't like what the AI generates?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "You have three options: (1) Regenerate - some builders let you regenerate with different prompts or settings, (2) Edit manually - change text, images, layout, colors using the visual editor, (3) Switch builders - try a different AI builder. Most beginners keep 70-80% of what the AI generates and customize the rest. The AI is starting point, not final product. If you absolutely hate the result, try a different prompt or switch builders entirely. Each AI has different strengths - Durable excels at local businesses, Mixo at landing pages, Squarespace at beautiful designs."
