          "text": "AI generation takes 30 seconds to 2 minutes. Total time to published site: 30 minutes to 2 hours for most beginners. Breakdown: AI generation (30 sec-2 min), text customization (15-30 min), image swapping (10-20 min), mobile testing (5-10 min), domain connection (5-15 min). First site takes longer due to learning curve. Second site typically takes 30-45 minutes total. Compared to traditional builders (4-8 hours minimum), AI is 8-16x faster. The speed is real - you can have a live site same-day you start. Most beginners launch their first site within 2 hours of signing up."
